      "title": "Set up",
      "content": "Line $l$ is parallel to $y = 8x + 4$, so it has slope $8$. It passes through the origin, giving equation $y = 8x$."
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve",
      "content": "Substitute the point $(6, d)$ into $y = 8x$: $d = 8(6) = 48$."
    },
